{"tid":2259042,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"知道自己可能就死 點算","createTime":"2020-10-26T13:19:12.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-26T17:46:19.000Z","uid":199574,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"ee9f6539c75eb46d89f127a7b9d80eeb29415729","tid":2259042,"uid":199574,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:19:12.000Z","msg":"好努力想令自己開心啲<br />\n明明身邊有好錫我嘅朋友<br />\n但我成日都會覺得得自己一個人<br />\n諗嘢越嚟越負面 <br />\n好想有人係我諗衰嘢嘅時候<br />\n俾個膊頭我喊下 攬下我<br />\n俾我放曬啲負面情緒岀嚟<br />\n<br />\n以往經歷過好多次同死亡擦身而過嘅時候<br />\n但今次 真係好怕<br />\n以為自己身體未去到咁差<br />\n但原來已經去到無得醫 無辦法<br />\n依幾日發夢都夢到自己死咗<br />\n<br />\n20年啦 捱得咁辛苦 最終都迎嚟依個結果<br />\n成日問點解係我<br />\n問點解所有最差嘅事都發生係自己身上<br />\n俾人拋棄 俾屋企拋棄 俾愛嘅人拋棄<br />\n要逼自己成長 逼自己做一個大人<br />\n真係好攰 好辛苦 好難捱"},{"pid":"0f13f7ab938b07a183c715f8367d2c6692be6044","tid":2259042,"uid":328316,"like":1,"dislike":4,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:20:51.000Z","msg":"88"},{"pid":"5b694126efd9861e1ddab8b38f2f34bf504ace68","tid":2259042,"uid":328316,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:21:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb696bc3c6e11fd43cf7b2235f0e15873cdd3bb4","tid":2259042,"uid":44209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:33:10.000Z","msg":"有絕症？"},{"pid":"cc3895e470761c78533976694aa7068f32192983","tid":2259042,"uid":70501,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T13:34:50.000Z","msg":"冇事嘅 大步欖過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/please.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"02e234758eb4c6d7fa40e344d6aa4fba24477895","tid":2259042